metadata.name: world's rektest dad  { access pass }
metadata.description:
```markdown  
# world's rektest dad { access pass }  
an homage to rektguy by 
  @OSF  
  @alienqueen  
  @Mando

## notes && things to know  
- this is a *digital access pass and utility token*  
- you will get guaranteed monthly airdrops if you hold this token 
- the first few airdrops will be homages to my favorite artists  
- then there will be original character art  
- there will be other editions  
- there will be 1/1s given away based on merit  
- when the discord officially opens, this pass will let you in  
- this pass will give the holder the highest single-token role in discord

### monthly airdrop edition  
- each address holding this pass will receive a monthly airdrop edition  
- if you hold 5 passes you'll get 5 tokens   
- each airdrop will have the same supply as this access pass  
- the first airdrop will be in the first few days of March

### other editions  
- occasionally other editions will drop  
- they will be announced in advance  
- they will have varying supply  
- they will allow you to join discord

### 1/1s  
- 1/1s will be occasionally airdropped to holders  
- 1/1s will usually be rewarded on merit (e.g. you spread the word on twitter or discord)  
- 1/1s also may be randomly dropped 
- the first 1/1 will drop in early March

### in the works  
- ERC-721 collections from original character art  
- website  
- gallery  
- discord  
... and more as I think of it

*p.s. the next drop will be an homage to @alienqueen*  
```
